short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: This extension enables you to use a softphone embedded in the Five9 Web application.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: The softphone extension is a Chrome/ Chromium browser extension supporting both Chrome and MS Edge browsers. It is code (mainly in JavaScript) that runs in the web browsers. It interacts with web pages in the browser and communicates to the softphone via local WebSockets.
